<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:652.20px" class="cls_006"><span class="cls_006">な</span><span class="cls_002">形容詞</span><span class="cls_012">  ［</span><span class="cls_009">／</span><span class="cls_012">］→</span><span class="cls_006">に</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:672.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">如上述般</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">改變形容詞的形式作為副詞使用。</span></div>
